edu.buffalo.cse562.checkpoint1

Class SqlToRA

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.buffalo.cse562.checkpoint1.SqlToRA

  • public class SqlToRA
extends java.lang.Object
    Convert the output of JSqlParser into a Schema.Database and Plan Most of the heavy lifting is done by two subclasses ParseSelect and ParseFrom which implement SelectVisitor and FromItemVisitor respectively.
